{"tid":2371244,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"急 狗狗突然震 焦躁不安 唔肯行","createTime":"2021-01-18T16:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T16:28:10.000Z","uid":306282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbcd145e5d4d0b99c30b67244ae09a2df66ddcf","tid":2371244,"uid":306282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"狗女 2歲 <br />\n突然心跳加速 全身震 好焦躁不安 不願意行走 叫佢試下行會盡量好快行完想快d坐低<br />\n2019年6月已試過一次<br />\n果時睇左醫生都搵唔到原因 照左x光 冇骨折 醫生只懷疑佢可能係腿部肌肉受傷 開左止痛藥<br />\n但當日返到屋企未食藥就突然回復正常 冇哂以上所有症狀<br />\n今日又突然變成咁樣 唔知點算<br />\n開緊post 時（持續左約半個鐘）又突然正常返<br />\n<br />\n唔知應該睇咩醫生 因為每次發病時間短 睇醫生都只係靠口述同影片 斷唔到症<br />\n狗狗好鍾意跑、玩 好擔心佢可能（心臟、神經）方面有問題以後都唔可以再跑... 各位有類似經驗、獸醫推介嗎... 好擔心 求求各位巴絲幫手"},{"pid":"a7bc3eeedcbc1d5140aa23c30425196536d71920","tid":2371244,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"搵師傅打堂齋啦 你屋企有嘢"},{"pid":"24351c49c9ca2eaac9d7e7144849ed6a6f7fd346","tid":2371244,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"乜品種？係咪椎間盤突出"},{"pid":"bd15a9ea4d40cb7c679ff42779ac0baa0dec7bce","tid":2371244,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"全身震好大機會係佢覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屋企果隻上個星期都係夜晚震曬唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初初以為佢凍親 <br />\n醫生一睇係脊骨發炎<br />\n打咗消炎針加食咗幾日藥就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈建議你轉獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者有機會係天氣引致嘅骨節痛<br />\n但詳細一定要睇獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好上連登問喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣荃灣廣場後面車房街果幾間都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以試試佢？"},{"pid":"65cfba8e78e623d9455eab40175b26d56d7e6699","tid":2371244,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7bc3eeedcbc1d5140aa23c30425196536d71920","tid":2371244,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"搵師傅打堂齋啦 你屋企有嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4007ee24aa73449c17d52f291e3db3a273731bea","tid":2371244,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7bc3eeedcbc1d5140aa23c30425196536d71920","tid":2371244,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:12:04.000Z","msg":"搵師傅打堂齋啦 你屋企有嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"先排除健康問題<br />\n先再向鬼神方向搵答案"}]}